{"tid":149412,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「置頂」你今日飲咗幾多杯水呀（2）","createTime":"2017-03-09T09:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T23:56:39.000Z","uid":48165,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1afa6e0d2c9fdc24fffa86620a1636e9603a0f9c","tid":149412,"uid":48165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"今日夠數未呀？ <br />\n<br />\n咩話？！淨係lunch 飲過半杯奶茶？！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老尾而家係咪制緊水無得俾你飲？<br />\n<br />\n提你飲水又好話我捽你數<br />\n<br />\n你估我想架咩？自己醒目少少啦<br />\n<br />\n你睇下隔離team 日日都爆數，個個痾啲尿白雪雪，連最廢個個 Peter 都飲左7杯 <br />\n<br />\n你呢？<br />\n<br />\n你個腎叫緊救命<br />\n<br />\n你膀胱乾哂塘<br />\n<br />\n你條脷有兩尺厚脷苔<br />\n<br />\n你口臭，你易攰，你作感冒，生暗瘡生飛滋<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你飲唔夠水呀仆街！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n啲水免費架！！！ 打開水龍頭就飲到瀨尿呀！！！健康就擺係你眼前垂手可得呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n點解唔飲多啲呀？！ 生性啲唔好衰俾人睇！ <br />\n<br />\n明白就渣渣淋去飲啦望！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重貼而推 From <span style=\"color: maroon;\">尾指長過食指</span>巴打"},{"pid":"ade89d7e8abf0b06428260858cd0b0c4a9340b92","tid":149412,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"懶得出去拎水杯"},{"pid":"1f645b01095d42434fe976a51a55cdb61b8ab5a5","tid":149412,"uid":48165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懶得出去拎水杯</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n咪玩啦大佬 ， 下次入房之前攞定囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f0df87ce4b43e88aa7bc406db5f1fea0be91c5","tid":149412,"uid":84815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"飲水好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a868ad42349b7eb89000c6040fd906523e3612","tid":149412,"uid":8174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"每個鐘飲700ml水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n坐得好近水機<img src=\"/assets/fa