/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aceccc569e3106fa839e426ef50f29294feb165","tid":149412,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:48:45.000Z","msg":"以前中學一眼訓或者曬就會飲水 每日攞住個一公升水樽番學 一定會斟滿多一次 番屋企又係狂飲<br />\n冬天就因為凍 所以成日斟熱水暖身 瘋狂去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家番個份工好少機會飲水 幾個鐘先飲一次 好唔慣"},{"pid":"b09043dc0913e72b3cd8e71f26b50785dd6df7ec","tid":149412,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前中學一眼訓或者<span style=\"color: red;\">悶</span>就會飲水 每日攞住個一公升水樽番學 一定會斟滿多一次 番屋企又係狂飲<br />\n冬天就因為凍 所以成日斟熱水暖身 瘋狂去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家番個份工好少機會飲水 幾個鐘先飲一次 好唔慣</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c1ef0b2f05ac4f8644ed00b5fae365193b092aa5","tid":149412,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"紀見到即飲返杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e236791df71de706531fd3205f15c46567e81650","tid":149412,"uid":48165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前中學一眼訓或者<span style=\"color: red;\">悶</span>就會飲水 每日攞住個一公升水樽番學 一定會斟滿多一次 番屋企又係狂飲<br />\n冬天就因為凍 所以成日斟熱水暖身 瘋狂去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家番個份工好少機會飲水 幾個鐘先飲一次 好唔慣</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁樣課上咗飲水一坐底有水樽就會係咁飲試過一次過飲一升飲到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但出街就可以好耐唔似"},{"pid":"206eb3f211d6e8ae9ca562bdad17502d0119714b","tid":149412,"uid":3004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"我飲幾多痾幾多<br />\n所以好唔鍾意飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}